  "texts": [
    "We will consider these questions in more depth in below.",
    "There are other philosophically important aspects of agenthood that we will not be considering.",
    "We won't be considering whether ChatGPT makes decisions, has or lacks autonomy, or is conscious; we also won't worry whether ChatGPT is morally responsible for its statements or its actions (if it has any of those).",
    "We will argue that even if ChatGPT is not, itself, a hard bullshitter, it is nonetheless a bullshit machine.",
    "The bullshitter is the person using it, since they (i) don't care about the truth of what it says, (ii) want the reader to believe what the application outputs."
  ],
